  "body": "Following the discussion from https://github.com/coredns/coredns/pull/2163\r\nI would like to had the support for username and password in the etcd configuration.\r\n\r\nIn the PR discussion @miekg said he would prefer to support this from the config file instead of some environment variable.\r\n\r\nI can work on that and provide a PR that implement that feature.\r\nIs there any other recommendation regarding this feature ?\r\n\r\nAbout the format of the config file, I was thinking implementing something like\r\n```\r\netcd [zone]{\r\n   endpoint http://localhost:2379\r\n   credentials username password\r\n}\r\n```\r\nI can also be more explicity and do \r\n```\r\netcd [zone]{\r\n   endpoint http://localhost:2379\r\n   username username\r\n   password password\r\n}\r\n```\r\nWhat do you think ?\r\n```\r\n```",
